snippet.title: Nova: Cloudwalker's Tale - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Nova: Cloudwalker's Tale is a puzzle game for PC currently in development by Racoon & Sheep.

The Cloudwalker must start a journey across forgotten civilizations to restore the world's cycle. Gather star shards and discover mysterious leyends on the remote regions of this land.

Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/RacoonAndSheep

novathegame.carrd.co
